<script>
export default {
    data(){
        return{
            todo:''
        }
    },
    methods:{
        submitHandler(){
            if(!this.todo) return
            this.$store.commit('ADD_TODO',{
                content:this.todo,
                complete:false
            })
            this.todo=''
        }
    }
}
</script>
<template src="./template.html"></template>
<style scoped src="./style.css"></style>
